      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">易經 13 初九</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">易經 13 初九</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>初九：同人于門，無咎。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The first NINE, undivided, (shows the representative of) the union of men just issuing from his gate. There will be no error.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
