      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>六二：同人于宗，吝。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The second SIX, divided, (shows the representative of) the union of men in relation with his kindred. There will be occasion for regret.</seg>
