      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>九三：伏戎于莽，升其高陵，三歲不興。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The third NINE, undivided, (shows its subject) with his arms hidden in the thick grass, and at the top of a high mound. (But) for three years he makes no demonstration.</seg>
      </tuv>
