      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>九五：同人，先號啕而后笑。大師克相遇。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>In the fifth NINE, undivided, (the representative of) the union of men first wails and cries out, and then laughs. His great host conquers, and he (and the subject of the second line) meet together.</seg>
